{"tid":2230406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒稱解放軍分析指日本將對華採取強硬戰略","createTime":"2020-10-05T01:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T08:39:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"38184d6d66e9fc448ca12c2cb88464a8d4e028cc","tid":2230406,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"日媒稱解放軍分析指日本將對華採取強硬戰略<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407835&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=a764cdf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407835&h=0a4937f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=407835</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】日本傳媒報道，中國軍方分析認為，日本新政府希望與美國等國家建立海洋聯盟，將會對中國採取強硬的戰略。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">共同社報道，中國軍方的專家於九月下旬的解放軍內部會議上，發表分析報告，指在九月中上台的菅義偉政府，希望在印太地區與美國等國家建立海洋聯盟，預料日本在國家安全問題上，將會採取強硬的對華戰略，因此中國有必要採取措施，對抗日本的圍堵。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道又指，中國軍方認為，菅義偉將會延續前首相安倍晉三的政策，目前正摸索對敵方基地擁有攻擊能力的可能性，意味日本一貫的「專守防衛」國防政策，將會出現變化，中國應視之為「新課題」，做好準備，不排除中國會加速強化軍備的可能。"},{"pid":"3da53b614724bae45b761a0a6c01863016b2267f","tid":2230406,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"有乜措施？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0940b06269d84c488580933ca1b41cebb04e3c5","tid":2230406,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得知佛山個偽日本街一收信就笠水啦"},{"pid":"aa1af191ecaa55ff92bbc70cc5445dc88f73ab91","tid":2230406,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:41:45.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de6ec84be8b74d2071067958b75513f03757b9d","tid":2230406,"uid":59461,"like